<p>Hello, <%= @user.email %>!</p>

<p>Someone requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.</p>

<p><%= link_to "Change my password", edit_password_reset_url(@token) %></p>

<p>This link will expire in <%= @expires_in_minutes %> minutes.</p>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email — your password won't change until you
access the link above and create a new one.</p>

<p style="color:#666;font-size:12px">
  Requested at <%= @requested_at.utc.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M UTC") %>
  from IP <%= @request_details[:ip_address] %>
  (<%= @request_details[:user_agent] %>)
</p>
